<title>Thinking Asynchronously</title>
<link>http://nodecasts.net/episodes/5-thinking-asynchronously</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://nodecasts.net/episodes/5-thinking-asynchronously</guid>
<description>&lt;div class=&quot;episode-description&quot; readability=&quot;9&quot;&gt;
&lt;p itemprop=&quot;description&quot;&gt;Asynchronous programming can be difficult if you're not used to it; we'll talk about some common patterns and pitfalls for working in an asynchronous environment. We'll also introduce a flow control library to handle multiple nested asynchronous operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

</description>
